close_reason: Cross-platform CI hardening passed in GitHub Actions run 25211328234; local focused and coverage verification passed; release tag v2026.5.1 remains unchanged at 61f6ac6.
body: GitHub Actions run 25210023872 failed after the 2026.5.1 release verification commit. macOS exposed path alias and file discovery count assumptions; Windows exposed path spelling and shell quoting assumptions. The fix must keep release artifacts unchanged and harden tests/workflow signal only.
